cons:
Contractor agency - Photon exploits contractors A LOT. 
1. Lowball salary (for junior designer, they provide 65K-75K in the beginning. unless you have other higher offer to bargain);
2. No salary growth even you get promoted and take more responsibilities;
3. Unfair agreement. They verbally agreed with sponsor H1B, but when you get selected, they FORCE you to sign another 2-year contract to continue their sponsorship. If you break the contract, you need to pay the compensation about $12000-$16000 depend on the contract.
